        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer546027321" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12198708541694847524">Often frowned upon for his militant atheism, Dawkins shines with optimism in this book. Instead of the attacks he is mostly known for, it is full of poetry and love songs for the world as he sees it: through science and the wonders that human intelligence has been able to unfold in the world.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


